  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I assume the reason is that Selma didn't speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left by ourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was thinking, because I worked before the war as a farmer, so I was thinking well, we'll try.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe we can get in this direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was nice people that I worked for them, they might be able to help me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was not too sure they would have helped us, but that's the only thing I could think of at the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that didn't work even this way because in mean time it got early in the morning, and we had to hide because then it's day, and we knew they were looking all over.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
